00:00:12.595 --> 00:00:15.473 position:50% align:center
[REONA] I think it's time
I come clean with you.

00:00:15.557 --> 00:00:18.101 position:50% align:center
You need to know the truth.

00:00:18.184 --> 00:00:20.687 position:50% align:center
What do you mean?

00:00:20.770 --> 00:00:21.855 position:50% align:center
Quick confession.

00:00:21.938 --> 00:00:23.898 position:50% align:center
If someone besides Kamui
beat the game,

00:00:23.982 --> 00:00:26.067 position:50% align:center
I'd lose all sense of restraint.

00:00:26.151 --> 00:00:29.904 position:50% align:center
I'm such a simp for winners
I'd probably marry them.

00:00:29.988 --> 00:00:32.032 position:50% align:center
Please tell me
you remember that.

00:00:32.115 --> 00:00:35.994 position:50% align:center
Uh, sure. As long as you
tell me it was only a joke.

00:00:36.077 --> 00:00:38.496 position:50% align:center
Well, um. Okay, here's the deal.

00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:41.166 position:50% align:center
Ten years ago,
I actually ran into Kamui.

00:00:41.249 --> 00:00:42.792 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:00:42.876 --> 00:00:44.210 position:50% align:center
'Course it was in-game.

00:00:44.294 --> 00:00:48.048 position:50% align:center
But the encounter made
no less of an impact.

00:00:48.131 --> 00:00:50.425 position:50% align:center
He was strutting through
town like a lion,

00:00:50.508 --> 00:00:52.635 position:50% align:center
clad in gorgeous black armor.

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:55.472 position:50% align:center
I was in high school in
those days, so naturally ,

00:00:55.555 --> 00:00:59.434 position:50% align:center
to say I was smitten would be
like saying water is wet.

00:00:59.517 --> 00:01:03.104 position:50% align:center
He swaggered toward the city
gates, ready to leave.

00:01:03.188 --> 00:01:05.357 position:50% align:center
I couldn't bear to see him go.

00:01:05.440 --> 00:01:10.820 position:50% align:center
So I did what anyone would do,
I asked him out.

00:01:14.616 --> 00:01:17.202 position:50% align:center
Sorry. I'm not into chicks
with the mammary glands

00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:18.787 position:50% align:center
of a Holstein heifer.

00:01:18.870 --> 00:01:20.246 position:50% align:center
Uh?!

00:01:20.330 --> 00:01:23.124 position:50% align:center
Sometimes too much of a
good thing is well and fine.

00:01:23.208 --> 00:01:26.336 position:50% align:center
But in your case, honey,
I'd have to hire a Sherpa.

00:01:26.419 --> 00:01:28.838 position:50% align:center
Bye-bye.

00:01:31.174 --> 00:01:33.343 position:50% align:center
Ugh! I had to look up "Sherpa."

00:01:33.426 --> 00:01:35.720 position:50% align:center
But can you imagine?
First, he says I'm a cow,

00:01:35.804 --> 00:01:37.931 position:50% align:center
then compares me to a
treacherous mountain range?

00:01:38.014 --> 00:01:40.475 position:50% align:center
And because I have a
soupcon of self-respect,

00:01:40.558 --> 00:01:42.852 position:50% align:center
when the bastard cleared
the unbeatable KQ,

00:01:42.936 --> 00:01:44.437 position:50% align:center
I vowed revenge!

00:01:44.521 --> 00:01:46.147 position:50% align:center
Hell hath no fury like me!

00:01:46.231 --> 00:01:49.776 position:50% align:center
I made it my mission
to see Kamui dethroned!

00:01:49.859 --> 00:01:54.280 position:50% align:center
Whoever beat him, I'd marry!
Or something.

00:01:55.824 --> 00:01:58.326 position:50% align:center
Wait, Is that the whole story?

00:01:58.410 --> 00:02:00.787 position:50% align:center
Indeed! Clear the game, Hiro!

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:02.163 position:50% align:center
Then propose to me!

00:02:02.247 --> 00:02:04.666 position:50% align:center
The wedding will be
nothing short of spectacular!

00:02:04.749 --> 00:02:07.085 position:50% align:center
We'll send Kamui
an engraved invitation.

00:02:07.168 --> 00:02:10.463 position:50% align:center
and then when we kiss,
we'll give him the finger!

00:02:10.547 --> 00:02:12.173 position:50% align:center
[HIRO grunts]

00:03:51.272 --> 00:03:53.566 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Well, that was a thing.

00:03:53.650 --> 00:03:55.819 position:50% align:center
Aren't secrets supposed
to be more profound?

00:03:55.902 --> 00:03:59.906 position:50% align:center
Seriously, that had to be the
most anti-climactic reveal ever.

00:03:59.989 --> 00:04:01.533 position:50% align:center
So much for inspired.

00:04:01.616 --> 00:04:04.452 position:50% align:center
Now I'm the opposite
of motivated.

00:04:05.453 --> 00:04:06.705 position:50% align:center
[HIRO exhales]

00:04:06.788 --> 00:04:08.790 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
Still awake, I see.

00:04:11.793 --> 00:04:13.420 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Tesla...

00:04:15.630 --> 00:04:18.633 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] My apologies
about Amos and Granada.

00:04:18.717 --> 00:04:22.095 position:50% align:center
No worries.
Honestly not a big deal.

00:04:22.178 --> 00:04:25.682 position:50% align:center
I'm, uh kinda surprised
to see you up this late.

00:04:25.765 --> 00:04:28.601 position:50% align:center
I daren't let my
vigilance waver.

00:04:28.685 --> 00:04:31.771 position:50% align:center
Sneak attack?
Perish the thought.

00:04:31.855 --> 00:04:35.150 position:50% align:center
The goblins'll make
their move in the morning.

00:04:35.233 --> 00:04:38.445 position:50% align:center
Er, just a hunch.

00:04:38.528 --> 00:04:40.447 position:50% align:center
